==乘客量==
根據港鐵向[[香港立法會|香港立法會]]提交的文件披露，輕鐵507綫早上繁忙時間載客率為93%。<ref>{{cite news|title=港鐵逼爆每一程 邊條綫載客率104%？|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160413/54982637|newspaper=蘋果日報 (香港)|date=2014-04-13|accessdate=2014-04-15|archive-date=2020-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511055247/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160413/54982637|dead-url=no}}</ref>

